## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **ME/CFS = NO FDA-approved treatment** (2026-05-08 기준 — 30+ year unmet need). ampligen (rintatolimod) Argentina 승인, US FDA reject 1995-2013, 재시도. quantum-VQE 의 mechanism 미정 한계 + biomarker 부재.
2. **long COVID = NO FDA-approved treatment** (RECOVER trial NIH 2024 진행중). nirmatrelvir-ritonavir Paxlovid PANORAMIC negative + RECOVER positive 2024 mixed result. quantum-VQE Mpro pocket leverage 가능 — 그러나 임상 endpoint 불확실.
3. **pregabalin Lyrica 2007** = first FDA fibromyalgia — α2δ subunit voltage-gated Ca channel. structural pocket VQE 가능. duloxetine 2008 + milnacipran 2009 SNRI cluster.
4. **ivabradine Corlanor 2015** = POTS 1L off-label — sinoatrial If channel (HCN). midodrine α1-AR + fludrocortisone + pyridostigmine AChE 모두 off-label POTS.
5. **low-dose naltrexone (LDN) 1.5-4.5 mg** = ME/CFS + FM + long COVID open-label evidence — opioid antagonist biased modulation. RCT 부재.
6. **abrocitinib + upadacitinib JAK inhibitor research long COVID** (cross-autoimmune) + **low-dose tocilizumab IL-6 long COVID research**. JAK + IL-6 axis cross-link autoimmune roadmap.
7. **BC-007 (Berlin Cures) anti-GPCR autoantibody apheresis-replacement** long COVID research. β-AR + M-AchR autoantibody hypothesis.
8. **coenzyme Q10 + NAD+ + L-carnitine supplement evidence weak** — mitochondrial dysfunction 가설 잔존, RCT-grade 부족.
9. **cryptocyte ATP / lactate metabolism mechanism research** — ME/CFS 의 erythrocyte deformability + ATP turnover anomaly 가설.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, chronic fatigue spectrum 의 multi-system mechanism modeling 한계 명확. raw#10 에 명확히 포함: ME/CFS = NO FDA-approved treatment + long COVID 동일 + 양자-VQE 의 mechanism 미정 한계 + 큰 unmet need.

